long_description:
# AdvTrains Train: DB BR 160 (E 60)

The DB Class 160 is a model by mbb of an electric shunter locomotive originally
designated Deutsche Reichsbahn class E60 and later Deutsche Bundesbahn 160. This
locomotive also has 4 passenger seats designated the *Engineers' Area*.

It has a wagon span of 3.0 m and can travel at 20 m/s (72 km/h)

[View this mod at the Train Catalogue](https://advtrains.de/wiki/doku.php?id=usage:trains:advtrains_db160)
